         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="  Manually  enter ASNs received via mail or fax.   ASNs received via EDI should automatically update the Purchase Order  in the system.  This will assist in  scheduling of receiving dock operations, aid in production planning/delivery  to point of use material operations.&#10;    The following information is required:   Ship date, ship quantity, supplier’s lot number, and tank  car/container number. "/>
